---
import SingleLayout from '@layouts/SingleLayout.astro'
import { getConfig } from '@libs/config'

export function getStaticPaths() {
  return [
    {
      params: { version: getConfig().docs_version }
    }
  ]
}
---

<SingleLayout title="Accessibility statement: Boosted documentation" description="">
  <h2 id="context">Context <a class="anchor-link" href="#context" aria-label="Link to this section: Context"></a></h2>
  <p>
    Orange undertakes to make its websites internet, intranet, extranet and its mobile applications accessible in
    accordance with article 47 of Law No. 2005-102 of February 11, 2005.
  </p>
  <p>
    To this end, it implements the following strategy and actions: <a
      href="https://gallery.orange.com/rse/?od=d4d15fea-9e7a-4497-8b04-c5e7f9290dca&om=b4e153e8-7460-4196-8890-a18eca5a51a9&v=sharedSelection#l=row&ss=3ba60f1d-f9fc-4b21-aca6-056dbdae6b94"
      >the pluri-annual accessibility framework</a
    >.
  </p>
  <p>This accessibility statement applies to the Boosted documentation.</p>
  <h2 id="conformity-level">
    Conformity level <a class="anchor-link" href="#conformity-level" aria-label="Link to this section: Conformity level"
    ></a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    &ldquo;Boosted Documentation&rdquo; is partially compliant to the criteria with <a
      href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG22/">WCAG version 2.2, level AA</a
    >.
  </p>
  <p>
    ORANGE SA refers to the WCAG international recommendations. <a
      href="https://a11y-guidelines.orange.com/fr/cadrage/correspondance-rgaa-wcag/"
      >Here is the correspondence link between the RGAA and the WCAG (French)</a
    >.
  </p>
  <p>The audit was carried out via <a href="https://la-va11ydette.orange.com/?lang=en">the Orange va11ydette</a>.</p>
  <h3 id="tests-result">
    Tests result <a class="anchor-link" href="#tests-result" aria-label="Link to this section: Tests result"></a>
  </h3>
  <div class="row summary">
    <div class="col-lg-3">
      <h4 class="pie" data-value="64">
        <span class="visually-hidden">Global compliance</span>
        <span class="pie-val">64%</span>
      </h4>
      <p class="lead">Global compliance</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-3">
      <h4 class="pie" data-value="87">
        <span class="visually-hidden">Average compliance</span>
        <span class="pie-val">87%</span>
      </h4>
      <p class="lead">Average compliance</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p>The compliance audit carried out by ORANGE SA reveals that:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>64% of WCAG level A and AA criteria are met.</li>
    <li>The average compliance rate of the online service is 87%.</li>
  </ul>
  <div class="table-responsive">
    <table class="table table-striped">
      <caption class="bd-caption">Summary by levels</caption>
      <thead
        ><tr>
          <th scope="row">Level</th>
          <th scope="col" class="text-center">A</th>
          <th scope="col" class="text-center">AA</th>
          <th scope="col" class="text-center">Total</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row">Number of criteria</th>
          <td class="text-center">32</td>
          <td class="text-center">24</td>
          <td class="text-center">56</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row">Compliant</th>
          <td class="text-center">9</td>
          <td class="text-center">12</td>
          <td class="text-center">21</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row">Non-compliant</th>
          <td class="text-center">7</td>
          <td class="text-center">5</td>
          <td class="text-center">12</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row">Not applicable</th>
          <td class="text-center">16</td>
          <td class="text-center">7</td>
          <td class="text-center">23</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row" class="table-active">Compliance</th>
          <td class="text-center table-active">56%</td>
          <td class="text-center table-active">71%</td>
          <td class="text-center table-active">64%</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <div class="table-responsive">
    <table class="table table-striped">
      <caption class="bd-caption">Compliance rate by pages according to the two levels of criteria A and AA</caption>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row">Criteria / Level</th>
          <th scope="col" class="text-center">Compliant / A</th>
          <th scope="col" class="text-center">Compliant / AA</th>
          <th scope="col" class="text-center">Non-compliant / A</th>
          <th scope="col" class="text-center">Non-compliant / AA</th>
          <th scope="col" class="text-center">Not applicable / A</th>
          <th scope="col" class="text-center">Not applicable / AA</th>
          <th scope="col" class="text-center table-active">Compliance rate</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row"><span class="visually-hidden">Page:</span>Home</th>
          <td>12</td>
          <td>13</td>
          <td>4</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>16</td>
          <td>9</td>
          <td class="table-active">81%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row"><span class="visually-hidden">Page:</span>Docs</th>
          <td>14</td>
          <td>13</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>3</td>
          <td>16</td>
          <td>8</td>
          <td class="table-active">84%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row"><span class="visually-hidden">Page:</span>Examples</th>
          <td>14</td>
          <td>14</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>16</td>
          <td>8</td>
          <td class="table-active">88%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row"><span class="visually-hidden">Page:</span>Design guidelines</th>
          <td>14</td>
          <td>15</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>1</td>
          <td>16</td>
          <td>8</td>
          <td class="table-active">91%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row"><span class="visually-hidden">Page:</span>Overview</th>
          <td>15</td>
          <td>13</td>
          <td>1</td>
          <td>3</td>
          <td>16</td>
          <td>8</td>
          <td class="table-active">88%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row"><span class="visually-hidden">Page:</span>Brand</th>
          <td>14</td>
          <td>14</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>16</td>
          <td>8</td>
          <td class="table-active">88%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row"><span class="visually-hidden">Page:</span>Translations</th>
          <td>15</td>
          <td>14</td>
          <td>1</td>
          <td>3</td>
          <td>16</td>
          <td>7</td>
          <td class="table-active">88%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row"><span class="visually-hidden">Page:</span>Cookies</th>
          <td>14</td>
          <td>13</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>16</td>
          <td>9</td>
          <td class="table-active">87%</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <h2 id="content-not-accessible">
    Content not accessible <a
      class="anchor-link"
      href="#content-not-accessible"
      aria-label="Link to this section: Content not accessible"></a>
  </h2>
  <p>The contents listed below are not accessible for the following reasons.</p>
  <h3 id="non-compliances">
    Non-compliances <a class="anchor-link" href="#non-compliances" aria-label="Link to this section: Non-compliances"
    ></a>
  </h3>
  <p>List of non-compliant WCAG criteria:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>1.1.1 Non-text Content, Level A</li>
    <li>1.3.1 Info and Relationships, Level A</li>
    <li>1.4.3 Contrast (Minimum), Level AA</li>
    <li>2.4.2 Page Titled, Level A</li>
    <li>2.4.3 Focus Order, Level A</li>
    <li>2.4.4 Link Purpose (In Context), Level A</li>
    <li>2.4.6 Headings and Labels, Level AA</li>
    <li>2.5.3 Label in Name, Level A</li>
    <li>2.5.8 Target size, Level AA</li>
    <li>3.1.2 Language of Parts, Level AA</li>
    <li>3.3.2 Labels or Instructions, Level A</li>
    <li>4.1.3 Status Messages, Level AA</li>
  </ul>
  <h2 id="establishment-of-this-accessibility-statement">
    Establishment of this accessibility statement <a
      class="anchor-link"
      href="#establishment-of-this-accessibility-statement"
      aria-label="Link to this section: Establishment of this accessibility statement"></a>
  </h2>
  <p>This declaration was established on 7/30/2024.</p>
  <h3 id="technical-specifications-of-the-site">
    Technical specifications of the site <a
      class="anchor-link"
      href="#technical-specifications-of-the-site"
      aria-label="Link to this section: Technical specifications of the site"></a>
  </h3>
  <ul>
    <li>HTML</li>
    <li>CSS</li>
    <li>JavaScript</li>
  </ul>
  <h3 id="testing-environment">
    Testing environment <a
      class="anchor-link"
      href="#testing-environment"
      aria-label="Link to this section: Testing environment"></a>
  </h3>
  <p>The verifications were performed with the following software combinations:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Edge 126.0</li>
    <li>Firefox 115.13</li>
  </ul>
  <h3 id="methods-and-tools-to-evaluate-accessibility">
    Methods and tools to evaluate accessibility <a
      class="anchor-link"
      href="#methods-and-tools-to-evaluate-accessibility"
      aria-label="Link to this section: Methods and tools to evaluate accessibility"></a>
  </h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Automatic testing:</strong> axe DevTools 4.83.0 (axe-Core 4.9.1), Wave 3.2.5.3</li>
    <li><strong>Functional testing:</strong> NVDA 2023.3.1, Keyboard navigation</li>
  </ul>
  <h3 id="pages-which-have-been-the-subject-of-compliance-verification">
    Pages which have been the subject of compliance verification <a
      class="anchor-link"
      href="#pages-which-have-been-the-subject-of-compliance-verification"
      aria-label="Link to this section: Pages which have been the subject of compliance verification"></a>
  </h3>
  <p>The verification audit was performed on the following pages using the Orange va11ydette:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Home: <a href="https://boosted.orange.com/">https://boosted.orange.com/</a></li>
    <li>Docs: <a href="https://boosted.orange.com/docs">https://boosted.orange.com/docs</a></li>
    <li>
      Examples: <a href="https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/examples/">https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/examples/</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      Design guidelines: <a href="https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/guidelines/"
        >https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/guidelines/</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      Overview: <a href="https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/about/overview/"
        >https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/about/overview/</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      Brand: <a href="https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/about/brand/"
        >https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/about/brand/</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      Translations: <a href="https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/about/translations/"
        >https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/about/translations/</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      Cookies: <a href="https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/about/cookies/"
        >https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.3/about/cookies/</a
      >
    </li>
  </ul>
  <h2 id="feedback-and-contact-information">
    Feedback and contact information <a
      class="anchor-link"
      href="#feedback-and-contact-information"
      aria-label="Link to this section: Feedback and contact information"></a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    If you are unable to access content or a service, you can contact the site manager to be directed to an accessible
    alternative or obtain the content in another form.
  </p>
  <p>
    We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of this site. Please let us know if you encounter accessibility
    problems by sending an email to <a href="mailto:accessibilite.france@orange.com">accessibilite.france@orange.com</a
    >.
  </p>
  <h2 id="legal-remedies">
    Legal remedies <a class="anchor-link" href="#legal-remedies" aria-label="Link to this section: Legal remedies"></a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    You have reported to the website manager an accessibility problem that prevents you from accessing content or one of
    the portal&rsquo;s services and you have not received a satisfactory response, in this case:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Write a message to the <a href="https://formulaire.defenseurdesdroits.fr/">Défenseurs des Droits</a>.</li>
    <li>
      Or contact the <a href="https://www.defenseurdesdroits.fr/saisir/delegues"
        >Défenseurs des Droits delegate in your department</a
      >.
    </li>
    <li>
      Or send a letter by post (free of charge, do not put a stamp):
      <address>Défenseur des droits<br />Libre réponse 71120<br />75342 Paris CEDEX 07</address>
    </li>
  </ul>
</SingleLayout>
